## 3. Función de autenticación

```sql
CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION fu_autenticar(
    p_username IN VARCHAR2,
    p_password IN VARCHAR2
) RETURN BOOLEAN IS
    v_count NUMBER;
BEGIN
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    INTO   v_count
    FROM   gena_usuario
    WHERE  UPPER(login)  = UPPER(p_username)
    AND    password_hash = TO_CHAR(ORA_HASH(p_password))
    AND    activo        = 'S';

    RETURN v_count > 0;
END;
```

